		<RichText x="66" y="1008" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="308" height="20" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">秘源护罩：70%生命值盾。击破后瘫痪15s。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="63" y="533" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ff9999" width="272" height="43" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" color="#ff9999">最后试炼机关</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ffb399" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="62" y="580" fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="20" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ff9999" width="205" height="25" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="20" fontStyle="italic" color="#ff9999">Final Trial Device</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ffb399" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深古秘源机龙.assets/Image_14.png')" x="64" y="64" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="431" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">秘源机龙立即进行划、砸2段普通攻击，依次造成<span color="#ffebbf">75%,70%</span><span>伤害；第二段攻击可与小龙共鸣展开护罩，遏制攻击行动。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="442" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">若上述技能被小龙遏制，则该爪与小龙将对峙10s，期间另外一爪化为大炮，持续向角色发射火球，造成<span color="#ff9999">30%</span><span>伤害。对峙结束后猛地造成</span><span color="#ffebbf">100%</span><span>伤害。对峙期间若进行5次攻击，可直接使护罩-85%。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深古秘源机龙.assets/Image_15.png')" x="720" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
