		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深古秘源机龙.assets/Image_18.png')" x="1268" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深古秘源机龙.assets/Image_19.png')" x="596" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深古秘源机龙.assets/Image_20.png')" x="576" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">秘源机龙朝场地内持续喷吐烈焰，逐渐造成<span color="#ff9999">15%,20%,30%</span><span>伤害；可与小龙共鸣展开护罩。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">秘源机龙先放射出大量金光织火命中玩家，均造成<span color="#ff9999">30%</span><span>伤害，随后将玩家禁锢，并逐渐持续造成</span><span color="#ffebbf">20%,30%,40%</span><span>伤害。需与小龙共鸣方可解除禁锢状态。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
