		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="423" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">秘源机龙初始持有<span textDecoration="underline">秘源护罩</span><span>，遭受小龙攻击时会额外失去</span><span color="#ffdfbf">15%</span><span>，且在小龙对峙期间尝试破盾则会令其直接损失</span><span color="#ffdfbf">85%</span><span>，护罩破坏后秘源机龙损失</span><span color="#ffbfbf">20%</span><span>生命值并瘫痪15s。</span></p>
			</content>
